业内最高。 这种大幅度的降价促销行为，虽然在一定程度上刺激了市场需求，促进了销量的增长，但其背后所隐藏的问题却不容忽视。 首先，价格战的持续进行意味着车企利润空间被不断压缩。为了争夺市场份额，车企不得不采取降价策略来吸引消费者。吉利杨学良：“卷”一日不消，中国汽车不会真正走遍全球_易车"},"attached_info":"CkAI8MyA8efRy5UsEAMaCTEwOTMxNTczMSC9iNO0BjAAOOcCQBVyCTY2MTY3MDU0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-10dad3ef7d76b68d6a1cf687676ad005_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1721949952.147648","card_id":"Q_662019683","target":{"id":662019683,"title":"如何看警察学校爆火，录取分数线已经六百多分了，直逼一流985？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662019683","type":"question","created":1721373337,"answer_count":119,"follower_count":335,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[15114,139132],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI8MyA8efRy5UsEAMaCTEwOTM5MzM2NCCZpei0BjAAOM8CQBZyCTY2MjAxOTY4M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7da6c3ad8ddaeef1e7e13e273cf97044_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1721949952.147855","card_id":"Q_662471382","target":{"id":662471382,"title":"如何评价漫威电影《死侍与金刚狼》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662471382","type":"question","created":1721812961,"answer_count":42,"follower_count":48,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,109576,209447,404595,3498261],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"Cj8I8MyA8efRy5UsEAMaCTEwOTQ5MzY5NyDhj4O1BjAAODBAF3IJNjYyNDcxMzgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/